*.pem
*.key
*.p8
*.p12
*.keystore
credentials.json

# Local planning / task notes (not for the public repo)
ai-crawlability-tasks.md
*-tasks.md
TODO.local.md

# Generated demo snapshots (built from demoEnvironment.ts — regenerated each build)
**/app/demo/snapshot.json
**/public/**/demo/snapshot.json

# Large 3D model assets — commit only the manifest (catalog.json), not binaries
**/public/models/*.glb
**/public/models/*.gltf
**/public/models/*.fbx
**/public/models/*.bin

